 rel=\"noopener\">《Shadow DOM 201：CSS 和样式》</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-family: Circular, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.28px; color: #666666; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">使用 :unresolved 伪类避免无样式内容闪烁（FOUC）</strong></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-family: Circular, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.28px; color: #666666; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">为了缓解<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background: 0px 0px; color: #26b89a; text-decoration: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.3s ease; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flash_of_unstyled_content\" target=\"_